dialogues.name: Yvonne
dialogues.content: Thank you, Vincent! Thanks to your help with tutoring in math, my grades have improved compared to before!

dialogues.name: Vincent
dialogues.content: You're welcome! Helping each other among classmates is only natural; I'm glad I could assist you!
